OL,3,CWildfire stretching nearly four miles
OL,4,Ccontained in UK's largest national park
OL,6,FFirefighters spent a second day trying
OL,7,Fto tackle the fire, which started in
OL,8,Fthe Cairngorms National Park in the
OL,9,FScottish Highlands. ITV News Scotland
OL,10,FReporter Louise Scott has the latest
OL,12,FA wildfire which stretched nearly four
OL,13,Fmiles in the Cairngorms National Park
OL,14,Fhas been contained, a Scottish
OL,15,FGovernment minister has said.
OL,17,FThe fire, which has been burning for
OL,18,Fmore than 24 hours, has led to
OL,19,Fevacuations of tourist sites and other
OL,20,Fproperties around Glenmore near
OL,21,FAviemore.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
