FL,316,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31502
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1784287145
OL,3,CWildfire stretching nearly four miles
OL,4,Ccontained in UK's largest national park
OL,6,FFirefighters say they are facing a
OL,7,F"protracted incident" as they seek to
OL,8,Fprevent the flames from spreading to
OL,9,Fother areas.
OL,11,FThe wildfire started in heathland at
OL,12,FRyvoan Bothy, near Nethy Bridge, late
OL,13,Fon Wednesday morning and stretched
OL,14,Fmore than 3.5km wide by Thursday
OL,15,Fmorning.
OL,17,FA number of homes and businesses,
OL,18,Fincluding campsites and ski resorts in
OL,19,Fthe Glenmore Forest Park area, have
OL,20,Fbeen closed and evacuated as a safety
OL,21,Fprecaution.
OL,26,@oD@AOUoD@UO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/13
