OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,316,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31503
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1784287145
OL,3,CWildfire stretching nearly four miles
OL,4,Ccontained in UK's largest national park
OL,6,FSmoke could be seen for miles around
OL,7,Fthe site of the fire on Thursday
OL,8,Fmorning, as at least four fire engines
OL,9,Fand other resources were tackling the
OL,10,Fblaze.
OL,12,FThere have been no reports of any
OL,13,Fcasualties.
OL,15,FThe RSPB, which runs the nearby Loch
OL,16,FGarten nature reserve, said
OL,17,Fapproximately 300 hectares of land
OL,18,Fhave been burnt so far.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/13
