OL,3,CWildfire stretching nearly four miles
OL,4,Ccontained in UK's largest national park
OL,6,FThe charity said 27 of its staff and
OL,7,Fvolunteers were out helping fight the
OL,8,Fblaze on Wednesday, using equipment
OL,9,Fincluding all-terrain vehicles with
OL,10,Fwater bowsers, backpack hoses and
OL,11,Fshovels.
OL,13,FIt added that there is an "urgent"
OL,14,Fneed for a firefighting helicopter.
OL,26,@uD@[OUuD@bO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
