PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1784287145
OL,3,CWildfire stretching nearly four miles
OL,4,Ccontained in UK's largest national park
OL,6,FDuncan Ferguson, operations manager at
OL,7,Fthe Spey Fishery Board, lives in
OL,8,FGlenmore, a village near Aviemore.
OL,10,FMr Ferguson said police came to his
OL,11,Fhouse on Wednesday afternoon, telling
OL,12,Fresidents to "leave your pets and go".
OL,14,FThe fire service has urged people to
OL,15,Favoid the area and also advised
OL,16,Fresidents in Aviemore, Glenmore and
OL,17,Fthe surrounding communities to keep
OL,18,Ftheir doors and windows closed due to
OL,19,Fthe smoke.
OL,26,@tD@NOUtD@eO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/13
