PN,31510
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1784287145
OL,3,CWildfire stretching nearly four miles
OL,4,Ccontained in UK's largest national park
OL,6,FGroup commander Raymond King said:
OL,7,F"While we want people to enjoy the
OL,8,Fgood weather, we ask that anyone in
OL,9,Fthe Cairngorms National Park near to
OL,10,FAviemore and Glenmore avoid the area.
OL,12,F"This part of the Cairngorms National
OL,13,FPark is popular with hillwalkers, and
OL,14,Fwe ask that people remain vigilant
OL,15,Fwhile active firefighting continues."
OL,26,@oD@AOUtD@AOUwD@eO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
