OL,3,CWildfire stretching nearly four miles
OL,4,Ccontained in UK's largest national park
OL,6,FCairngorms National Park Authority
OL,7,Fsaid firefighters have been working
OL,8,Fwith landowners to contain the
OL,9,Fincident and create fire breaks, with
OL,10,Fhigh winds causing the fire to spread
OL,11,Facross areas of trees and woodland.
OL,13,FA spokesperson for the authority said:
OL,14,F"The ongoing incident near Ryvoan
OL,15,FBothy is deeply concerning, and we are
OL,16,Fgrateful to all those who are working
OL,17,Fto tackle the fire.
OL,26,@vD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G11/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,316,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31512
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1784287145
OL,3,CWildfire stretching nearly four miles
OL,4,Ccontained in UK's largest national park
OL,6,F"We would echo the advice of SFRS to
OL,7,Favoid the area while firefighters and
OL,8,Fpartners work to bring this blaze
OL,9,Funder control.
OL,11,F"This incident ` alongside wildfires
OL,12,Fwe are seeing across the UK this week
OL,13,F` serves as a stark reminder of the
OL,14,Frisks that periods of drier, hotter
OL,15,Fweather can pose."
