CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1784287145
OL,3,CWildfire stretching nearly four miles
OL,4,Ccontained in UK's largest national park
OL,6,FThe blaze comes while parts of
OL,7,FScotland are at a very high risk of
OL,8,Fwildfire over the next few days.
OL,10,FThe SFRS, in conjunction with the
OL,11,FScottish Wildfire Forum, has issued
OL,12,Fwildfire warnings for the central
OL,13,FHighlands, southern and eastern
OL,14,FScotland.
OL,16,FThe alert, warning of a very high risk
OL,17,Fof wildfire, came into force on
OL,18,FWednesday and lasts until Monday.
OL,20,FIt follows days of hot and dry weather
OL,21,Fin many parts of the country.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G13/13
